<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Lal Isu Ka Nei Tai</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lei Lalpuon lopi chu dawng intin,
 Lei pakcha hawih cheng le vuoi ina;
 I damlai niu hi le hung tum ngei ngei ina,
 Aw heh, Lal Isu chu ka nei tai.

[V2]
 Lili pak hawih Lal Isu ka nei,
 Kei di'n a pak kumsawt gam hawih ah;
 Gimumna-ah aman ei umpih ina,
 Lili pak hawih Lal Isu ka nei.

[V3]
 2. A lungsietna gam vak hawih achun,
 Amah chu Zingdawng Sawl No ahi;
 Gimthei in, lei ahin liengvai in um mahleng,
 A gam noma ei pui ding ei nai.

[V4]
 3. Tuhin kapin um tadih leng le,
 Thihna ni chu ka hung chan tieng leh;
 Lau ta puong ie, thana um ei kaitho in tin,
 Ka mitthi ei thiek hul sak tana.

[V5]
 4. Ka guol deihten zie khawvel ahin,
 Ei nusieh un ka lung a hel ie;
 Lungkham, puong ie thawmhau a ka um lai hin le,
 Lili pak hawih Isun ei umpih.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>175</hymn_number>
<author>C.Z Huala</author>
</song>